# AI Copilot — Cursor rules

## Read first
- AGENTS.md — stack, commands, conventions
- Cursor_Guide.md — execution checklist pointer
- docs/COMPREHENSIVE_RULES_AND_GUIDELINES.md

## Code principles
- Minimal scope: smallest correct diff; no drive-by refactors
- Match existing naming, imports, and file layout
- Backend Python 3.12+ in `backend/.venv`; never rely on system Python 3.9 for tests
- Frontend: React 19 + Vite; run `npm --prefix frontend run build` after TSX changes

## Servers
- Use `./scripts/server.sh` (backend 8500, frontend 5177 strictPort)
- Do not invent alternate ports or auto-increment behavior

## Testing
- `cd backend && .venv/bin/pytest` for backend
- Monkeypatch native OS dialogs in tests; Finder E2E is manual on macOS only
- See docs/TESTING.md

## Verification before "done"
- docs/VERIFICATION_RULES.md
- docs/QUALITY_GATEWAY.md
- docs/TASK_VERIFICATION_TEMPLATE.md

## Git
- Do not commit unless the user explicitly asks
- Never commit `.env`, secrets, or `backend/app.db`
